  "text": "To confirm the identity of both chicken TNF receptors, we performed phylogenetic analysis of these two genes with the receptors from other vertebrates. Both chicken candidate TNFR1 and TNFR2 (Figure 3 ) receptors cluster with high bootstrap support with the corresponding TNF receptors from reptiles and mammals [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
